{
  "id": 5198951632470016,
  "name": "Algorithm Updates in WebCrypto",
  "summary": "Add post-quantum cryptography and a common symmetric AEAD to the set of cryptographic algorithms available in the Web Cryptography API. This will enable developers to have access browser-provided implementations of common quantum-resistant cryptographic algorithms standardized by NIST.\n\n* ML-KEM - 768, 1024\n* ML-DSA - 44, 65, 87\n* ChaCha20-Poly1305\n* X-Wing",
